            "login": "ConcaveTrillion"
          },
          "body": "Approach: Structure as a `Groom` class that accepts a `gh` adapter object (real uses subprocess; tests use FakeGh). Entry point `main()` instantiates the real adapter and calls `run_all()`. Return value from `run_all()` is a dict: `{\"actions\": [...], \"judgment_queue\": [...]}` — printed as JSON to stdout.\n\nPlan: docs/superpowers/plans/2026-05-17-gh-workflow-plan-c-grooming.md#groom-auto-impl\nVerification: `uv run pytest tests/scripts/test_groom_auto.py -v` — all green\nTracks: #57\n\nAcceptance:\n- [ ] All 15 tests in Task 1 pass\n- [ ] Script is executable (`chmod +x`)\n- [ ] `python scripts/groom-auto.py --help` runs without error\n- [ ] `BLOCKED_BY_RE = re.compile(r'Blocked by:\\s*#(\\d+)', re.IGNORECASE)` matches body format\n- [ ] PyYAML used for frontmatter parsing (not regex)\n- [ ] `archive_referenced_research` checks both `docs/superpowers/specs/` and `docs/superpowers/decisions/` for any mention of the research filename",
